{"tid":469874,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)潛行兇間 幽靈車神","createTime":"2017-11-15T18:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T21:57:58.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4ed1601c96b8e0f80ababf1697ba6dc4194132c","tid":469874,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:10:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=mVBMGW%2F4qRvfiGhMNBV%2FNQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=66cc2228\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=mVBMGW%2F4qRvfiGhMNBV%2FNQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f0f36fb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7f/Inception_ver3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7f%2FInception_ver3.jpg&h=5f1f2cea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/ea/Ghost_Rider.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fea%2FGhost_Rider.jpg&h=8009b454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.唐姆&middot;柯柏（Dominick &quot;Dom&quot; Cobb；李奧納多&middot;狄卡皮歐飾）是一名「盜夢者」（extractor），與搭檔亞瑟（Arthur）利用潛意識進入別人夢境竊取商業機密。於一次任務中，柯柏與亞瑟入侵日本國際企業老闆齋藤（Saito）的夢境意識，但柯柏的已故妻子茉兒（Mal）於夢中出現使任務失敗。齋藤事後透露自己是有意讓他們潛入以考驗二人技術，並安排了一個任務予他們<br />\n<br />\n2.火爆強尼(尼古拉斯&middot;凱奇 飾)原本是一個摩托車特技演員，為了拯救他父親的生命，他將自己的靈魂出賣給惡魔梅菲斯特(彼得&middot;方達 飾)，然而邪惡的勢力竟讓他走火入魔，化身為被詛咒的惡靈戰警，所到之處都引燃熊熊烈焰。而強尼漸漸開始學習控制自己的能力，將無法抑制的憤怒發洩在為非作歹的歹徒身上。但他情不自禁愛上了一個追逐他新聞的女記者(伊娃&middot;曼德絲 飾)，卻因失去靈魂飽受痛楚折磨；而他又將如何對抗更大的惡魔勢力呢?<br />\n<br />\n2 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=mVBMGW%2F4qRvfiGhMNBV%2FNQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=831d6f24\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=mVBMGW%2F4qRvfiGhMNBV%2FNQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=35241599\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b64ae0fcfc55b7bb74afb54d30ca9de480f86b5","tid":469874,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba8054c58b9dac27fd2370d6764240decd22b64","tid":469874,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25342f754c207f07d71a6d848040443ee44f1224","tid":469874,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c6